          "contents": "import pandas as pd\nimport matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n\n# Read the dataset\ndata = pd.read_csv('Titanic.csv')\n\n# Explore the dataset\nprint(data.info())\nprint(data.describe())\nprint(data.head())\n\n# Step 2 - Group the data\n\n\n# Step 3 - Generate a stacked bar chart\n\n\n\n",
